result.title: 2016 - 2016 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) Phytoplankton functional groups data derived from in-situ flow cytometry as part of the Ferrybox on the RV Cefas Endeavour in the North and Celtic seas in 2016 and 2017.
result.name: 2016-2016-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-phytoplankton-functio-2017
result.notes:
These data contain information on the abundance and fluorescence of 6 
phytoplankton functional groups based on flow cytometry measurements. The data 
covers 3 surveys on the RV Cefas Endeavour, CEND12_16, CEND04_17, and 
CEND19_17 in the North and Celtic Seas.
